td.p:
These requests for a preliminary ruling concern the interpretation of Article 2(1), (1a), (6) and (19), Article 7(4) and Article 9(1) and (2) of Directive 97/67/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 15 December 1997 on common rules for the development of the internal market of Community postal services and the improvement of quality of service (
OJ 1998 L 15, p. 14
), as amended by Directive 2008/6/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 20 February 2008 (
OJ 2008 L 52, p. 3
) (‘Directive 97/67’).
